The '''Happy Spacer''' was an intoxicant retailer owned by the [[Teltior]] [[Loeerna]] located in [[The Life]] section of the [[Vergesso Base]]. It sold various forms of intoxicating substances, including simple [[Salt/Legends|salt]], [[Lum/Legends|lum]], and [[Spice liquor/Legends|spice liquor]].

